@startuml activity_procure_to_stock
' Business process: Procure-to-stock - template section 2.2.3
|Purchase Staff|
start
:Create Purchase Order (status OPEN);
:Submit for approval;
|Purchase Manager / Accountant|
if (Approve?) then (yes)
  :Set PO = APPROVED;
else (no)
  :Set PO = REJECTED;
  stop
endif
|Warehouse Staff|
:Create Goods Receipt for PO;
:Enter accepted quantity,\nmanufacture & expiry dates;
:Confirm Goods Receipt;
|System|
:Increase inventory (weighted avg cost);
:Create Inventory Lot (FEFO);
:Write Inventory Transaction (RECEIPT);
if (All PO items fully received?) then (yes)
  :Set PO = COMPLETED;
else (no)
  :PO stays APPROVED\n(partial receiving);
endif
stop
@enduml
